WEBVTT

00:01:00.028 --> 00:01:01.902
Yana unda uchumi wetu.

00:01:01.926 --> 00:01:03.918
Yana unda jamii yetu.

00:01:03.942 --> 00:01:05.585
Serikali hazijui cha kufanya.

00:01:05.609 --> 00:01:07.625
Sasa hivi, zinaitikia.

00:01:07.649 --> 00:01:10.943
Na nina hofu kua tukishindwa,
kama raia --

00:01:10.967 --> 00:01:15.715
ambao ni, kwa maoni yangu,mguu
wa muhimu zaidi kwenye kigoda hicho --

00:01:15.739 --> 00:01:17.261
usichukue jukumu letu

00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:18.478
halafu ndo utapatia.

00:01:18.502 --> 00:01:23.263
Wapinzani, au watu wanaokuambia
kua biashara itafanikiwa, wamepatia.

00:01:23.287 --> 00:01:24.438
Itatokea.

00:01:24.462 --> 00:01:28.294
BF: Kwahio unasema kua watu
watalazimisha biashara

00:01:28.318 --> 00:01:30.826
au biashara italazimika kua
na majibu,